rows.label: qst104501_msg0001
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff... You smell
strong, mo! Are you strong?
You are strong, mo?

rows.label: qst104501_msg0002
rows.name:
Sorry, mo. It was rude of Kukn to
sniff you all of a sudden, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0003
rows.name:
Kukn has a very good nose, mo. My
nose has never failed me, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0004
rows.name:
Kukn's nose told me to open a
new shop in Temperantia, mo!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0005
rows.name:
But since no one else has
opened a shop, Kukn doesn't
know a safe trade route, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0006
rows.name:
Kukn judged that it would be too
dangerous to lead my friends safely
with only my nose to guide us, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0007
rows.name:
So, Kukn was sniffing around
for someone strong to be a
bodyguard and help out, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0008
rows.name:
Out of the 100 people Kukn sniffed,
you smelled the strongest, mo!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0009
rows.name:
Please, mo! Kukn wants you to
help us set up our shop, mo.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0011
rows.name:
Kukn will be waiting at
Overlook Hill in Temperantia,
so please come, mo!
